self.model = DiscreteMNL(solver='lbfgs', fit_intercept=True, est_stderr=
    True, reg_method='l2', alpha=0, l1_ratio=0, tol=0.0001, max_iter=100,
    coef=None, stderr=None, classes=None)
self.model.fit(self.data_spector.exog[4:5, :], self.y[4:5,], sample_weight=0.5)
np.testing.assert_array_equal(self.model.coef, np.zeros((4, 1)))
np.testing.assert_array_almost_equal(self.model.loglike_per_sample(self.
    data_spector.exog[4:6, :], np.array(['foo', 'foo'])), np.array([0, 0]),
    decimal=3)
np.testing.assert_array_almost_equal(self.model.loglike_per_sample(self.
    data_spector.exog[4:6, :], np.array(['foo', 'bar'])), np.array([0, -np.
    Infinity]), decimal=3)
